description: If you're a huge London CHE soccer fan, this is the app for you!  London CHE Soccer Fans provides you with access to the latest news, videos, stats, standings and scores. You'll always know what's happening with the club!   Plus you’ll find detailed team, roster and schedule information, so you’ll always be the most knowledgeable football fan in the room.   You can also discuss the latest news, results and highlights with other London CHE fans using the built in chat feature. Make sure your voice is heard!   There is no better or more comprehensive tool to stay up to date with London CHE. If you are a true fan, you owe it to yourself to download London CHE Soccer Fans today!    ** Arctic Gerbil Creations, Brighthouse Labs, and the London CHE Soccer Fans application are in no way associated with FIFA, the Premier League or the Championship.
